videos.description: No. 13 Kentucky star Rhyne Howard tallies a season-high 33 points, with 25 coming in the fourth quarter and OT, to beat No. 12 Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Rhyne time: Howard drops 25 in 4th/OT to top MS State
